                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d233">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">860C.01B11/19: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Acting Secretary of State</gloss> to
                        the Chargé to the Polish Government in Exile</hi> (<persName type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">Schoenfeld</hi>
                    </persName>), <hi rend="italic">at London</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1940-11-13T16:00:00-05:00"
                            >November 13, 1940—4 p.m.</date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>4. Your Polish Series No. 3, November 11, 3 p.m. In replying to the note of the
                    Polish Foreign Minister dated November 9, regarding the appointment of Mr.
                    Ciechanowski, you may include the following: <quote rend="blockquote">
                        <p>“The Government of the United States is pleased to learn that the Polish
                            Government agrees to the suggestion that Dr. Ludwig Rajchman and other
                            Polish officials on special mission at present in the United States
                            shall be recalled from the United States and expresses the hope that the
                            removal of Dr. Rajchman and these officials from this country shall take
                            place before the arrival of the newly appointed Ambassador.”</p>
                    </quote>
                </p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Welles</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
